Description: Comfortable four-bedroom duplex apartment AVAILABLE NOW, Laundry in the Unit, many renovated! It features four bedrooms, a nice kitchen, a dining room, a living room, one bathroom, and a separate basement. Hardwood floor throughout, and the condition is good! Laundry is in the unit, private, and no fee is charged. Quiet and convenient location, close to T, many stores and restaurants around. A must-see!
